name: Scandinavian_Lifestyle_Anita_Solid_Pine_Bookcase
reviews: Great for use as a pantry which I needed. Just a little trouble putting it together but it all worked out well. Would order another one but no room for it.
Well built and sturdy but has a pink hue. Was disappointed because I wanted white.
